INSERT INTO [BusinessSafe].[dbo].[StatutoryResponsibilityTemplate]([Id], [SectorId],[ResponsibilityCategoryId],[Title],[Description],[GuidanceNote],[ResponsibilityReasonId], [TaskReoccurringTypeId],[CreatedBy],[CreatedOn],[Deleted]) VALUES (15,1,5,'Gas Appliances','Check that the annual gas safety checks have been carried out and the equipment is safe to use.','3-5',2,5, N'4CC5B9B8-E335-4E27-9AA3-C48B9AA6BC4D', '2013-07-23 15:00:00.000', 0)
INSERT INTO [BusinessSafe].[dbo].[StatutoryResponsibilityTemplate]([Id], [SectorId],[ResponsibilityCategoryId],[Title],[Description],[GuidanceNote],[ResponsibilityReasonId], [TaskReoccurringTypeId],[CreatedBy],[CreatedOn],[Deleted]) VALUES (16,1,5,'Portable electrical equipment','Check and record that portable electrical equipment and power supply leads are free from defects and remain safe for use. Depending on the outcome review the frequency required for this check.','4-1',1,5, N'4CC5B9B8-E335-4E27-9AA3-C48B9AA6BC4D', '2013-07-23 15:00:00.000', 0)
