INSERT INTO [BusinessSafe].[dbo].[StatutoryResponsibilityTemplate]([Id], [SectorId],[ResponsibilityCategoryId],[Title],[Description],[GuidanceNote],[ResponsibilityReasonId], [TaskReoccurringTypeId],[CreatedBy],[CreatedOn],[Deleted]) VALUES (18,1,5,'Lifts','Check that statutory inspections have been completed and lifts remain fit for use. 6 monthly inspections for passenger lifts, annual inspection for goods only lifts.','4-18, 4-19',2,4, N'4CC5B9B8-E335-4E27-9AA3-C48B9AA6BC4D', '2013-07-23 15:00:00.000', 0)
